data.description: Welcome to Kinwood. This stunning two-story home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bath and a flex room previously used as an additional bedroom. Downstairs, the residence boasts a formal living, dining room, eat-in kitchen, living room with a masonry fireplace, office area and a downstairs flex room/bedroom with additional space. Upstairs, you will find three bedrooms and two full baths. The property has a large single-car garage, sun room, porch and a spacious backyard. Conveniently located next to Methodist University, it offers easy access to I295, Fort Bragg, and Liberty. VA Assumable with a 3.125% interest rate.
